Class MidiRouter.Listing

    MidiRouter

    protected abstract class MidiRouter.Listing
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements java.awt.event.MouseListener
    This represents a cell in the source or destinations column.

    The MIDI devices represented by these cells must be defined using a MidiDevice object.

    Author:
    Bradley Ross

      • Listing

        @Deprecated
public Listing​(javax.sound.midi.MidiDevice.Info info)
        Deprecated. 
        Specify the MIDI device using a MidiDevice.Info object.

        This is deprecated since {@link MidiSystem.getMidiDevice(MidiDevice.Info)} can't be relied upon to identify a single device, especially when dealing with synthesizers and sequencers. The problem may be related to software MIDI devices.

        Parameters:
        info - identifies MIDI device
